ğŸ•’ Cron Job Timing Examples

* * * * * echo "Hello" >> cron.log â†’ run every minute

0 * * * * echo "Hourly task" >> cron.log â†’ run hourly

0 0 * * * echo "Daily task" >> cron.log â†’ run daily

0 0 * * 0 echo "Weekly task" >> cron.log â†’ run weekly

0 0 1 * * echo "Monthly task" >> cron.log â†’ run monthly

0 6 * * 1-5 echo "Weekdays 6AM task" >> cron.log

ğŸ“‘ Special Cron Operators

@reboot echo "Run after reboot" >> cron.log

@hourly echo "Run every hour" >> cron.log

@daily echo "Run daily" >> cron.log

@weekly echo "Run weekly" >> cron.log

@monthly echo "Run monthly" >> cron.log
